{"tid":593841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【dc狗現晒形】的哥罷駛 消委會同日指的士用App揀客","createTime":"2018-03-15T10:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T11:42:01.000Z","uid":166571,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"76236df416b608fbd99ca58e628f266ea74261bd","tid":593841,"uid":166571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"罷駛都專業少少啦...得個3 40架的士喺到獻世<br />\n揀客仲大大聲認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/182520_0509d5647b8c8c173c6ea144211f4678.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F182520_0509d5647b8c8c173c6ea144211f4678.jpg&h=edebff0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/182846_ea36886ae4ced492c228d6a42b8d5aa3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F182846_ea36886ae4ced492c228d6a42b8d5aa3.JPG&h=52004340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/182853_172134e5965c61ca102e9196dce749d9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F182853_172134e5965c61ca102e9196dce749d9.JPG&h=be5eccda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係不解釋...<br />\n<br />\n近40輛的士今早（15日）於金鐘政府總部外進行的士慢駛行動，聲言要「Uber滾出香港」，炮轟白牌車搶飯碗。不過，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>消委會同日指出，不少的士司機愛透過網約車App揀客</strong></span>。到底一眾的士司機又點睇？<br />\n<br />\n的士司機楊先生直言：「佢（白牌車）真係搶咗我一半飯碗！」他說Uber收費比的士高昂，服務質素較好亦屬理所當然，有時一張單已等於不少的士司機半天的收入：「我由朝早做到依家，我都做唔到呢個數！」<br />\n<br />\n不少市民投訴的士司機揀客問題嚴重，消委會今日亦指出不少的士司機透過網約車App揀客。駕駛的士5年的王先生說，自己加入了3個網約的士平台，每日大約接幾張單。他大讚網約平台既方便乘客，又方便司機：「啲客知道有車嚟緊喺度等佢，安心好多。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不過他又坦言，使用網約App難免揀客︰「有得揀都揀個好啦，仲揀24蚊咩！」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n想知更多的士司機睇法？即刻睇片！<br />\n---------------<br />\n《港呢啲》：大事小事騎呢事，東網嚴謹選題，輕鬆製作！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/GzvQRx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FGzvQRx&d=rqW3Wev6K7EAcOQsoXcOev9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=9fbd1137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/GzvQRx</a>"},{"pid":"ce890fe06308a32ab6f0c00e33c1a85688754563","tid":593841,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbe91003c66981f194cf9a722177c2e743ead12","tid":593841,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968725becf3eb8edb99c8548ba28578d716810d5","tid":593841,"uid":92983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"一秒現形"},{"pid":"440bf83661481a2bd756b2a99b21c9b1449f138b","tid":593841,"uid":60074,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"乜撚野的哥，又帶頭用蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbae04398741baa870eb67d3b2ed427c5202abb","tid":593841,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:34:45.000Z","msg":"成班DC9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b860b899194cb63d52ad14f61f580c742d1f4e7","tid":593841,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:34:49.000Z","msg":"等幾個鐘一個客都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6811d44092dda5e8b89c64c8c56ec97b7b098ed","tid":593841,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"Dc狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\